After installing terrafom 

create new dir ex:demo

in demo folder create games.tf file with the following content

resource "local_file" "foo" {
  filename = "/root/event.txt" #path and name of the file want to create
  content = "World cup evenet 2021"
}

from this folder in bash terminal excute the following command 

#to download required plug-ins
terraform init

#to check whether the execution plan for a configuration matches your expectations before provisioning or changing infrastructure.
terraform plan

#to reach desired state / configuration 
terraform apply

check the file event.txt hasbeen created in specified path
